                <footer>
                    <p>
                        Any authorizations made from your Twitter accounts can be revoked in Twitter's App settings here: <a href="https://twitter.com/settings/applications" target="_blank">https://twitter.com/settings/applications</a>.
                    </p>
                </footer>
            </article>
